    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0

    v2 = wp.cos(0.88)
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.cos(tmp + 0.95) / v0))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.exp(v1 + 0.42)))
    v2 = v2
    tmp = wp.abs((v0 + 0.43))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos((v2 + 0.23 - v2 + 0.51)))
